  "task_html": "<div class=\"task-block task-blue\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Info: m und b aus dem Graphen ablesen</div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:flex-start;\">\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 200\" style=\"width:180px;flex-shrink:0;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:8px;background:#fafafa;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <line x1=\"10\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"100\" stroke=\"#cbd5e1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n      <line x1=\"100\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"100\" y2=\"190\" stroke=\"#cbd5e1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n      <line x1=\"10\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"10\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"75\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#d97706\"/>\n      <text x=\"107\" y=\"73\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#d97706\" font-family=\"monospace\">b = 3</text>\n      <text x=\"140\" y=\"38\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2563eb\" font-family=\"monospace\">m =</text>\n      <line x1=\"120\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"80\" stroke=\"#dc2626\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,2\"/>\n      <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"55\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"80\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,2\"/>\n      <text x=\"133\" y=\"93\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#dc2626\" font-family=\"monospace\">+2</text>\n      <text x=\"163\" y=\"72\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#16a34a\" font-family=\"monospace\">+1</text>\n      <text x=\"104\" y=\"195\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-family=\"monospace\">x</text>\n      <text x=\"12\" y=\"103\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-family=\"monospace\">y</text>\n    </svg>\n    <div style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\">\n      1. <strong>b</strong> ablesen: Wo schneidet die Gerade die y-Achse?<br>\n      2. <strong>m</strong> berechnen: Steigungsdreieck einzeichnen &rarr; m = &Delta;y &divide; &Delta;x\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:14px 0 8px 0;\"><strong>Aufgabe:</strong> Lies m und b aus den beschriebenen Graphen ab.</p>\n\n<div class=\"tbl-wrap\">\n  <table>\n    <thead><tr><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">Beschreibung</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">m</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">b</th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr><td class=\"given\">Schnitt bei y=2, geht durch (1|4)</td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2\" placeholder=\"m\"></td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2\" placeholder=\"b\"></td></tr>\n      <tr><td class=\"given\">Schnitt bei y=5, geht durch (2|3)</td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"-1\" placeholder=\"m\"></td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"5\" placeholder=\"b\"></td></tr>\n      <tr><td class=\"given\">Schnitt bei y=0, geht durch (3|6)</td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2\" placeholder=\"m\"></td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0\" placeholder=\"b\"></td></tr>\n      <tr><td class=\"given\">Schnitt bei y=&minus;1, geht durch (4|1)</td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.5\" placeholder=\"m\"></td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"-1\" placeholder=\"b\"></td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkStation(5)\">&#x2713; &#xDC;berpr&#xFC;fen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetStation(5)\">&#x21BA; Zur&#xFC;cksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-5\"></span>\n</div>",
  "sol_html": "<div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;line-height:2.2;\">\n  Schnitt y=2, P(1|4): m=(4&minus;2)/(1&minus;0)=<strong>2</strong>, b=<strong>2</strong><br>\n  Schnitt y=5, P(2|3): m=(3&minus;5)/(2&minus;0)=<strong>&minus;1</strong>, b=<strong>5</strong><br>\n  Schnitt y=0, P(3|6): m=(6&minus;0)/(3&minus;0)=<strong>2</strong>, b=<strong>0</strong><br>\n  Schnitt y=&minus;1, P(4|1): m=(1&minus;(&minus;1))/(4&minus;0)=<strong>0,5</strong>, b=<strong>&minus;1</strong>\n</div>"
}
